<subSubSection id="2BF24ACA1F5DFFA6FFEBFC11FBFB376E" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" type="description">
<paragraph id="635719411F5DFFA6FFEBFC11FEA8370F" blockId="22.[113,649,1008,1129]" box="[113,258,1008,1034]" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">DESCRIPTION</paragraph>
<paragraph id="635719411F5DFFA6FFEBFBEEFBFB376E" blockId="22.[113,649,1008,1129]" lastBlockId="22.[674,1213,216,1129]" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">
Arbustes (
<quantity id="A410B4A41F5DFFA6FF73FBF1FE98372D" box="[233,306,1040,1066]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" unit="m" value="2.5" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="1.0">1-4 m</quantity>
) à feuilles sessiles ou subsessiles (pétiole assez dégagé, pouvant atteindre quelques mm, dans le cas de 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FE21FBB1FC7033F5" authority="M.Schmid" authorityName="M. Schmid" authorityYear="2012" box="[443,986,216,1129]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="sessilifolium" status="var. nov." variety="ouazangouense">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FE21FBB1FDFD376E" box="[443,599,1103,1129]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T. sessilifolium</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FD3FFF38FCE733F5" box="[677,845,217,242]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">ouazangouense</emphasis>
M.Schmid
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel id="4AAF78281F5DFFA6FC73FF39FBFF33F5" box="[1001,1109,216,242]" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" rank="variety">var. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
). Limbe généralement parcheminé à subcoriace, rarement presque membraneux (
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FC09FEF9FCB43256" authority="M.Schmid" authorityName="M. Schmid" authorityYear="2012" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="sessilifolium" status="var. nov." variety="calcicolum">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FC09FEF9FB883236" box="[915,1058,279,305]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T. sessilifolium</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FBCAFEF6FB103236" box="[1104,1210,279,305]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">calcicolum</emphasis>
M.Schmid
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel id="4AAF78281F5DFFA6FCB6FED6FC243256" box="[812,910,311,337]" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" rank="variety">var. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FC01FED9FB073255" authority="Guillaumin" authorityName="Guillaumin" box="[923,1197,311,338]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aragoense">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FC01FED9FBB43256" box="[923,1054,312,337]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T. aragoense</emphasis>
Guillaumin
</taxonomicName>
), ou franchement coriace (
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FC2DFEB6FB1F3277" authority="M.Schmid" authorityName="M. Schmid" authorityYear="2012" box="[951,1205,342,368]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ateouense" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FC2DFEB6FB9C3277" box="[951,1078,343,368]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T. ateouense</emphasis>
M.Schmid
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel id="4AAF78281F5DFFA6FD3FFE96FD563296" box="[677,764,375,401]" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
), arrondi ou attenué en pointe obtuse au sommet, parfois rubané sur une grande partie de sa longueur vers la base (
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FC10FE57FBB432C8" box="[906,1054,437,463]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sessilifolium">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FC10FE57FBB432C8" box="[906,1054,437,463]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T. sessilifolium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FBB3FE57FD7E32F7" authority="Mez" authorityName="Mez" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="squarrosum">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FBB3FE57FB1332C8" box="[1065,1209,438,463]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T. squarrosum</emphasis>
Mez
</taxonomicName>
), légèrement panduriforme (
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FC6CFE37FB2532E8" box="[1014,1167,469,495]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="amplexicaule">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FC6CFE37FB2532E8" box="[1014,1167,469,495]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T.amplexicaule</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) ou falciforme (
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FCBAFE17FC1E3108" box="[800,948,502,527]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="squarrosum">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FCBAFE17FC1E3108" box="[800,948,502,527]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T. squarrosum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), arrondi à la base, en se partageant plus ou moins nettement en deux lobes embrassant ou non la tige (s’atténuant en angle aigu dans le cas de 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FCA4FDB4FB0D3169" authorityName="M. Schmid" authorityYear="2012" box="[830,1191,596,623]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="sessilifolium" variety="ouazangouense">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FCA4FDB4FC7D3169" box="[830,983,596,622]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T. sessilifolium</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FB96FDB4FB0D3169" box="[1036,1191,597,622]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">ouazangouense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
). Inflorescences terminales sur des rameaux normaux ou spéciaux (ordinairement ou occasionnellement selon les espèces), en panicule 2(-3) fois ramifiée. Fleurs longues de 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F5DFFA6FCFDFD33FC7F31EA" box="[871,981,722,749]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.75" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="2.5" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" unit="mm" value="2.75" valueMax="3.0" valueMin="2.5">2,5-3 mm</quantity>
(
<quantity id="A410B4A41F5DFFA6FC7EFD33FB9731EA" box="[996,1085,722,749]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.5" metricValueMax="5.0" metricValueMin="4.0" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" unit="mm" value="4.5" valueMax="5.0" valueMin="4.0">4-5 mm</quantity>
dans 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FBE6FD32FC11300B" authority="Schmid, 2012" authorityName="M. Schmid" authorityYear="2012" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="sessilifolium" status="var. nov." variety="calcicolum">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FBE6FD32FCA7300B" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T. sessilifolium</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FCD2FD13FC11300B" box="[840,955,754,780]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">calcicolum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="4AAF78281F5DFFA6FC5EFD12FB80300A" box="[964,1066,755,781]" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" rank="variety">var. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
), à pédicelle filiforme long de 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F5DFFA6FCE8FCF3FC7B302A" box="[882,977,786,813]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" metricValueMax="8.0" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" unit="mm" value="5.0" valueMax="8.0" valueMin="2.0">2-8 mm</quantity>
(longueur moyenne différant suivant les espèces), de couleur blanche à rose sur le vivant (rouge dans 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FB8BFCB3FB3E306C" box="[1041,1172,850,875]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aragoense">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FB8BFCB3FB3E306C" box="[1041,1172,850,875]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T. aragoense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), à ornementation glanduleuse généralement discrète. Style filiforme, atténué vers le haut, long de 1,5- 2,5(- 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F5DFFA6FD46FC51FC8F30CC" box="[732,805,944,971]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" unit="mm" value="5.0">5 mm</quantity>
). Axes des inflorescences en général finement et profondément ridés-sillonnés, légèrement et éparsement verruqueux (relativement lisses dans 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FC87FBF1FC37372E" box="[797,925,1040,1065]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aragoense">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FC87FBF1FC37372E" box="[797,925,1040,1065]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T. aragoense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
). Fruits globuleux de (4-) 5-8 (-10) mm de diamètre (inconnus dans le cas de 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FD5CFBB1FCEE376E" authority="Schmid, 2012" authorityName="M. Schmid" authorityYear="2012" box="[710,836,1104,1129]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ateouense" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FD5CFBB1FCEE376E" box="[710,836,1104,1129]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T. ateouense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="4AAF78281F5DFFA6FCD6FBAEFC0A376E" box="[844,928,1103,1129]" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
et 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F5DFFA6FC5BFBB1FBEA376E" box="[961,1088,1104,1129]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="22" pageNumber="301" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aragoense">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F5DFFA6FC5BFBB1FBEA376E" box="[961,1088,1104,1129]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="301">T. aragoense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
